  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BioCarbon Fund (BioCF)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Fund will provide technical assistance for REDD+ implementation and measures which improve the enabling environment for private sector investment; offer a finance for Verified Emission Reductions associated with avoided deforestation; and secures private sector finance, for example through purchasing commitments for sustainable commodities produced in the jurisdiction (sometimes called &#x2018;offtake agreements&#x2019;). Each country programme under the BioCarbon Fund will operate at the jurisdiction-scale, that is within a landscape-wide area that is governed by a single political jurisdiction.</narrative>
  </description>
